profile: GJ MacRae Foundation Repair are pioneers in the basement waterproofing and foundation repair industry with over 40 years of experience and 10,000+ issued waterproofing warranties to date. We don't just issue a document but truly provide the most reliable and time-tested waterproofing warranty available today in the GTA. We offer a wide range of above and below grade concrete waterproofing and interior/exterior weeping tile and sump box solutions coupled with industry leading structural repair methodologies and a safe, robust and high quality approach to underpinning and foundation wall replacements. See what the GJ MacRae difference is all about!
service_area:
We are located at 470 Winston Churchill Blvd., and presently service all of the GTA.

Toronto, North York, East York, Scarborough, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Oakville, Burlington, Milton and Brampton. In the north, Markham, Unionville, Thornhill and Woodbridge.
services: Waterproofing and Structural Foundation Repair Specialists
specialities: Basement Waterproofing, Structural Foundation Repair and Bench, Overflow and Underpinning Systems.
